data.description: Enjoy owning this wonderful 7-bed, 3-bath residence in the gated Entrada Bonita Community! The modern great room with wood-look flooring in all the right places offers warmth and grandeur. You'll love the chef's kitchen boasting recessed lighting, glossy stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, cabinetry with crown moulding, granite counters, and a center island equipped with a breakfast bar. Adding to the home's unique charm is a cozy den for work or play and a large loft with balcony access. The bright primary retreat includes plush carpet, a private ensuite with dual sinks, and a walk-in closet. Create lasting memories in the spacious backyard, providing a covered patio, gazebo, fire pit, and pavers.  The garage features an outlet to charge an electric vehicle.  Don't let this amazing opportunity pass you by!
